how/131646532.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/ruined-his-face-looksmaxxing-streamer-clavicular-brutally-roasted-after-unrecognizable-surgery-reveal/articleshow/131646532.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-11T05:52:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131646532,imgsize-420604.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA["Erica was described as an emotional asset": Candace Owens keeps pressure on officials over controversial Erika Kirk email]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131646512.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Candace Owens says she is intensifying her FOIA fight over a controversial White House Correspondents’ Dinner email that allegedly described Erika Kirk as an “emotional asset” shortly after a shooting incident. Owens claimed government departments initially rejected her request as too broad, prompting her team to submit a narrower version with specific names and dates. She also accused Andrew Colvett and others of misleading the public, insisting the leaked email is authentic and will eventually be verified.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/erica-was-described-as-an-emotional-asset-candace-owens-keeps-pressure-on-officials-over-controversial-erika-kirk-email/articleshow/131646512.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/erica-was-described-as-an-emotional-asset-candace-owens-keeps-pressure-on-officials-over-controversial-erika-kirk-email/articleshow/131646512.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-11T05:31:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131646512,imgsize-52308.cms